# AI Image Prompts for Tea-Infused Rice Blog Post

## Hero Image (Featured)
**File:** hero.jpg
**Prompt:** 
A beautiful overhead shot of a traditional Japanese ochazuke bowl on a wooden table. Steam rises gently from hot green tea poured over white rice. The bowl contains flaked salmon, nori strips, sesame seeds, and a pickled plum. Soft natural morning light, shallow depth of field, warm tones, food photography style, minimalist Japanese aesthetic, 4K resolution.

## Cultural Comparison Image
**File:** chafan-vs-ochazuke.jpg
**Prompt:**
Split composition showing Chinese chafan on the left and Japanese ochazuke on the right. Left side: rustic Chinese ceramic bowl with green tea rice, pickled vegetables, salted egg, wooden chopsticks. Right side: elegant Japanese lacquer bowl with sencha tea rice, salmon, nori, ceramic spoon. Traditional table settings, cultural contrast, warm ambient lighting, editorial food photography.

